<p>
<lb n="1"/>[[r]]ā<hi rend="grantha">ja</hi>kecaripanmarāna cakkara[[va]]ttikaḷ <hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi> kolo ‡ toṅka ‡ coḻateva[[ṟ]]ku yāṇṭu patiṉ Aiñcāvatu vaṭakarai Uttu<unclear>ṅ</unclear>[[ka]]tuṅkavaḷanāṭṭu
<lb n="2"/>yāvatu Ivvūr pavitti[[ramā]]ṇikkap pereriyi ‡ <unclear>ṉ</unclear> ki<unclear>ḻ ni</unclear> ‡ rnilattu Iraṇamukarāmaṉ tūmpukku kiḻakku māṉak kūṟu nilam mukkāṇi nikki Ita[[ṉ kiḻa]]kkum teṉpāṟke
<lb n="3"/>vāṇakovaraiya[[ṉ cu]]ttamallaṉ U ‡ ttama ‡ coḻaṉṉāṉ Ilaṅke<hi rend="grantha">śvara</hi>ṉeṉ Itu pa<hi rend="grantha">nmā</hi>ye<hi rend="grantha">śvara rakṣai</hi>
</p>

</div>

